ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Alberta Fishery Regulations, 1998
PrecisRegulations Amending the ALBERTA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1998 in order to further restrict the possession of live fish taken by anglers, modify the fine amounts for several offences where the current fines are not considered appropriate, and respond to concerns of the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations by adding clarity to the French version of the Regulations.
